[27/05/2019 13:08:31] <font color="#ffff00">pero son necesarias.</font>
[27/05/2019 13:08:33] <font color="#00ffff">¿Por qué?</font>
[27/05/2019 13:08:34] <font color="#ffff00">¿Por qué?</font>
